  "text": "Dependency Dashboard\n\nThis issue lists Renovate updates and detected dependencies. Read the [Dependency Dashboard](https://docs.renovatebot.com/key-concepts/dashboard/) docs to learn more.<br>[View this repository on the Mend.io Web Portal](https://developer.mend.io/github/vuejs/core).\n\n## Deprecations / Replacements\n> [!WARNING]\nThese dependencies are either deprecated or have replacements available:\n\n| Datasource | Package | Replacement PR? |\n|------------|------|--------------|\n| npm | [conventional-changelog-cli](https://redirect.github.com/conventional-changelog/conventional-changelog) | ![Unavailable](https://img.shields.io/badge/unavailable-orange?style=flat-square) |\n\n## Awaiting Schedule\n\nThe following updates are awaiting their schedule. To get an update now, click on a checkbox below.\n\n - [ ] <!-- unschedule-branch=renovate/build -->chore(deps): update build (`@vitejs/plugin-vue`, `esbuild`, `rollup-plugin-dts`)\n - [ ] <!-- unschedule-branch=renovate/lint -->chore(deps): update lint (`eslint-plugin-import-x`, `lint-staged`, `typescript-eslint`)\n - [ ] <!-- unschedule-branch=renovate/all-minor-patch -->chore(deps): update all non-major dependencies (`pnpm`, `pnpm/action-setup`, `pug`, `sass`)\n - [ ] <!-- unschedule-branch=renovate/test -->chore(deps): update test (`@vitest/coverage-v8`, `@vitest/eslint-plugin`, `puppeteer`, `vitest`)\n - [ ] <!-- unschedule-branch=renovate/dawidd6-action-download-artifact-18.x -->chore(deps): update dawidd6/action-download-artifact action to v18\n - [ ] <!-- unschedule-branch=renovate/major-build -->chore(deps): update dependency vite to v8\n - [ ] <!-- create-all-awaiting-schedule-prs -->🔐 **Create all awaiting schedule PRs at once** 🔐\n\n## Detected Dependencies\n\n<details><summary>github-actions (9)</summary>\n<blockquote>\n\n<details><summary>.github/workflows/autofix.yml (4)</summary>\n\n - `actions/checkout v6`\n - `pnpm/action-setup v4.2.0` → [Updates: `v4.4.0`]\n - `actions/setup-node v6`\n - `autofix-ci/action 7a166d7532b277f34e16238930461bf77f9d7ed8`\n\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>.github/workflows/ci.yml (3)</summary>\n\n - `actions/checkout v6`\n - `pnpm/action-setup v4`\n - `actions/setup-node v6`\n\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>.github/workflows/close-cant-reproduce-issues.yml (1)</summary>\n\n - `actions-cool/issues-helper v3`\n\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>.github/workflows/ecosystem-ci-trigger.yml (3)</summary>\n\n - `actions/github-script v8`\n - `actions/github-script v8`\n - `actions/github-script v8`\n\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>.github/workflows/lock-closed-issues.yml (1)</summary>\n\n - `dessant/lock-threads v6`\n\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>.github/workflows/release.yml (3)</summary>\n\n - `actions/checkout v6`\n - `pnpm/action-setup v4`\n - `actions/setup-node v6`\n\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>.github/workflows/size-data.yml (4)</summary>\n\n - `actions/checkout v6`\n - `pnpm/action-setup v4.2.0` → [Updates: `v4.4.0`]\n - `actions/setup-node v6`\n - `actions/upload-artifact v7`\n\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>.github/workflows/size-report.yml (9)</summary>\n\n - `actions/checkout v6`\n - `pnpm/action-setup v4.2.0` → [Updates: `v4.4.0`]\n - `actions/setup-node v6`\n - `dawidd6/action-download-artifact v14` → [Updates: `v18`]\n - `juliangruber/read-file-action v1`\n - `juliangruber/read-file-action v1`\n - `dawidd6/action-download-artifact v14` → [Updates: `v18`]\n - `juliangruber/read-file-action v1`\n - `actions-cool/maintain-one-comment v3`\n\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>.github/workflows/test.yml (13)</summary>\n\n - `actions/checkout v6`\n - `pnpm/action-setup v4.2.0` → [Updates: `v4.4.0`]\n - `actions/setup-node v6`\n - `actions/checkout v6`\n - `pnpm/action-setup v4.2.0` → [Updates: `v4.4.0`]\n - `actions/setup-node v6`\n - `actions/checkout v6`\n - `actions/cache v5`\n - `pnpm/action-setup v4.2.0` → [Updates: `v4.4.0`]\n - `actions/setup-node v6`\n - `actions/checkout v6`\n - `pnpm/action-